divs: Sighting DetailsMy wife and i noticed these lights that kept blinking off and on and at great distances at times.There was sometimes one and at times the three like in the pic. They where anywhere from Bartow all the way towards Lake Wales. This would last between 7:45pm and 10:00pm. I did get video but not close enough to reveal what they actually were. These started sometime in September and ended about the middle of November. this pic included has the three lights and the street light at the bottom left.
Summary: these strange lights that kept going off and on and sometimes at different areas in a very large radius
